Description:
.NET Conf 2025 Student Zone is designed to inspire and educate students about the latest innovations in .NET, with a special focus on CLI, AI, Copilot, Aspire, gaming, career opportunities, and the open nature of .NET. The event will showcase hands-on demos using both VS Code and the new Visual Studio, with sessions on Mac and Linux to highlight cross-platform capabilities.
